						CatureMe
Name   : CaptureMe
License: GPL3 (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html), FFmepeg and Zenity have their receptive license, please see their man page
Author : Salih Emin
Email  : salihemin (at) about.me 
Date   : 14-7-2011
Version: 1.1
System : Linux with Zenity and FFmpeg packages preinstalled
WebSite: http://screen-captureme.blogspot.com

						Description:
This simple script will use FFmpeg to make a video from your screen or a selected window. To use this app You need to have installed in your Linux distribution the FFmpeg and Zenity packages. After that you just doubleclick and then follow on-screen instructions.
